Direct Known Subclasses:
IndexedNameMap
public abstract class BaseIndexedMap<Key,Value> extends BaseMap<Key,Value> implements Iterable<Value>, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.collection.Indexable<Value>, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.collection.Addable<Value>
A map that allows access to data by both index and key. Note that LinkedHashMap preserves the order of values in the map, but it does not allow indexing of the map.
